Name: Ashes of Oahu
About the game: Ashes of Oahu is an open world, story driven shooter where you work with or against the surviving factions of a post apocalyptic Hawaii. Inspired by native Hawaiian stories, traditions, and beliefs but with a unique fictional twist that brings in ghosts, raiders, and gods Four distinct factions to work for...or against! Over 11,000 lines create a massive and engaging narrative Choices truly matter and can lead to any one of over 100 different endings! Guns take on new and amazing powers thanks to the Magical Weapon Mod System Play your way by unlocking 50+ skills and abilities 25 sq/km of beautiful locations throughout Oahu, Hawaii Craft items from Hawaiian resources you find throughout the island
